"src=\"\" data-caption=\"Toto je popisek\" /&gt;</code></li>\n"
"    "
"<li><code>&lt;video src=\"\" data-caption=\"Drupal Dance\" "
"/&gt;</code></li>\n"
"    <li><code>&lt;blockquote data-caption=\"Dries "
"Buytaert\"&gt;Drupal je úžasný!&lt;/blockquote&gt;</code></li>\n"
